<!-- 定義與症狀 -->
'''乳癌'''是由[[乳房|乳房]]組織發展成的[[癌症|癌症]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Breast Cancer|url=http://www.cancer.gov/cancertopics/types/breast|publisher=[[美国国家癌症研究所|National Cancer Institute]]|accessdate=2014-06-29|archive-date=2014-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140625232947/http://www.cancer.gov/cancertopics/types/breast|dead-url=no}}</ref>。乳癌的徵象包括乳房腫塊、乳房形狀改變、皮膚[[酒窩|凹陷]]、乳頭分泌物或是皮膚出現紅色鱗屑狀斑塊<ref name=NCI2014Pt>{{cite web|title=Breast Cancer Treatment (PDQ®)|url=http://www.cancer.gov/cancertopics/pdq/treatment/breast/Patient/page1/AllPages|publisher=National Cancer Institute|accessdate=2014-06-29|date=2014-05-23|archive-date=2014-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140705110404/http://www.cancer.gov/cancertopics/pdq/treatment/breast/Patient/page1/AllPages|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而出現遠端轉移的病患，可能會有{{link-en|骨痛|Bone pain}}、[[淋巴結|淋巴結]]腫大、[[呼吸困難|呼吸困難]]或[[黃疸|黃疸]]的情形<ref>{{cite book|last1=Saunders|first1=Christobel|last2=Jassal|first2=Sunil|title=Breast cancer|date=2009|publisher=Oxford University Press|location=Oxford|isbn=9780199558698|chapter=Chapter 13|edition=1st|url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=as46WowY_usC&pg=PT123|access-date=2014-12-18|archive-date=2014-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022054318/http://books.google.ca/books?id=as46WowY_usC&pg=PT123|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

<!-- 成因與診斷 -->
乳癌的風險因子包含了：[[肥胖症|肥胖症]]、缺乏運動、飲[[醇|酒]]、[[更年期|更年期]]時的[[激素替代療法|激素替代療法]]、[[游離輻射|游離輻射]]、[[月經|初經]]提早開始與晚生或不生育<ref name=NCI2014Pt /><ref name=WCR2014>{{cite book|title=World Cancer Report 2014|date=2014|publisher=World Health Organization|isbn=9283204298|chapter=Chapter 5.2}}</ref>。大約5至10%的病例是因父母親的[[遺傳|遺傳]]而發生。這些遺傳因子包含了[[BRCA1|BRCA1]]、[[BRCA2|BRCA2]]與其他因子。乳癌最常發生於供應母乳的[[乳腺|乳腺]]或乳葉內側。如果發生在乳腺，則稱做{{link-en|非特殊型侵襲性導管癌|ductal carcinoma|乳腺癌}}，發生在乳葉的則稱為{{link-en|乳葉癌|Lobular carcinoma}}<ref name=NCI2014Pt />。此外，乳癌還分成18個子類型。部分乳癌會先從{{link-en|癌前狀態|Precancerous condition}}開始發展，例如{{link-en|原位導管癌|Ductal carcinoma in situ}}<ref name=WCR2014 />。診斷方面，通常會針對腫瘤進行[[活體組織切片|活體組織切片]]來確診。如果確診，就會進行進一步檢測，確認乳癌是否發生擴散與治療方式<ref name=NCI2014Pt />。

<!-- 篩檢與治療 -->
{{link-en|乳腺癌篩檢|Breast cancer screening}}究竟是否有益仍具有爭議性。2013年[[考科藍合作組織|考科藍合作組織]]的評論，認為[[乳房攝影術|乳房攝影術]]是否有益還是有害，目前還不清楚<ref name=Got2013>{{cite journal | author = Gøtzsche PC, Jørgensen KJ | title = Screening for breast cancer with mammography | journal = The Cochrane database of systematic reviews | volume = 6 | pages = CD001877 | date = 2013-06-04 | pmid = 23737396 | doi = 10.1002/14651858.CD001877.pub5 }}</ref>。2009年，{{link-en|美國預防服務工作組|United States Preventive Services Task Force}}的評論認為，有證據顯示乳房攝影術對於40至70歲的婦女有益<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Nelson|first1=HD|last2=Tyne|first2=K|last3=Naik|first3=A|last4=Bougatsos|first4=C|last5=Chan|first5=B|last6=Nygren|first6=P|last7=Humphrey|first7=L|title=Screening for Breast Cancer: Systematic Evidence Review Update for the US Preventive Services Task Force [Internet]|date=Nov 2009|pmid=20722173}}</ref>，並建議50至74歲的婦女每兩年檢驗一次<ref name=USPSTFScreen2009>{{cite web|title=Screening for Breast Cancer|url=http://www.uspreventiveservicestaskforce.org/uspstf/uspsbrca.htm|work=US Preventative Services Task Force|accessdate=2012-12-24|date=December 2009|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130102015424/http://www.uspreventiveservicestaskforce.org/uspstf/uspsbrca.htm|archive-date=2013-01-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。對於有高風險的人，[[太莫西芬|太莫西芬]]或[[雷洛昔芬|雷洛昔芬]]等藥物可用於預防乳癌發生。 {{link-en|預防性乳房切除術|Preventive mastectomy}}也是部分高風險婦女可以採用的預防措施<ref name=WCR2014 />。如果得到乳癌，會使用數種治療方式，包含：[[外科學|手術]]、[[放射線療法|放射線療法]]、 [[化學療法|化學療法]]與[[標靶治療|標靶治療]]<ref name=NCI2014Pt />。乳癌手術的種類，從{{link-en|乳房保留手術|Breast-conserving surgery}}到[[乳房切除術|乳房切除術]]，有不同的手術方式<ref name="ACSfive">{{Citation |date = September 2013 |title = Five Things Physicians and Patients Should Question |publisher = {{tsl|en|American College of Surgeons||American College of Surgeons}} |work = {{tsl|en|Choosing Wisely||Choosing Wisely}}: an initiative of the {{tsl|en|ABIM Foundation||ABIM Foundation}} |page =  |url = http://www.choosingwisely.org/doctor-patient-lists/american-college-of-surgeons/ |accessdate = 2013-01-02 |archive-date = 2013-10-27 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131027085747/http://www.choosingwisely.org/doctor-patient-lists/american-college-of-surgeons/ |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=NCI2014TxProf>{{cite web|title=Breast Cancer Treatment (PDQ®)|url=http://www.cancer.gov/cancertopics/pdq/treatment/breast/healthprofessional/page1/AllPages|publisher=National Cancer Institute|accessdate=2014-06-29|date=2014-06-26|archive-date=2014-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140705110521/http://www.cancer.gov/cancertopics/pdq/treatment/breast/healthprofessional/page1/AllPages|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在手術當下或數日之後，可能會進行[[乳房重建|乳房重建]]。若乳癌中的癌細胞已擴散到其他身體部位的病患，則改以提高生活品質而非積極治療為主要的目標<ref name=NCI2014TxProf />。

<!-- 預後與流行病學 -->
乳癌的預後依癌症的類型、[[癌症分期|癌症分期]]以及病患年紀有所不同<ref name=NCI2014TxProf />。在[[已開發國家|已開發國家]]中，病患的存活率較高<ref name=WCR2008>{{Cite web |publisher=[[国际癌症研究机构|International Agency for Research on Cancer]] |year=2008 |title=World Cancer Report |url=http://www.iarc.fr/en/publications/pdfs-online/wcr/2008/wcr_2008.pdf |accessdate=2011-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720232417/http://www.iarc.fr/en/publications/pdfs-online/wcr/2008/wcr_2008.pdf |archive-date=2011-07-20 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>；在英國和美國，[[五年存活率|五年存活率]]可達八成到九成<ref name=UK2013Prog>{{cite web |title = Cancer Survival in England: Patients Diagnosed 2007–2011 and Followed up to 2012 |url = http://www.ons.gov.uk/ons/dcp171778_333318.pdf |website = Office for National Statistics |accessdate = 2014-06-29 |date = 2013-10-29 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141129124915/http://www.ons.gov.uk/ons/dcp171778_333318.pdf |archivedate = 2014-11-29 }}</ref><ref name=SEER2014/>。在发展中國家中，存活率則稍差<ref name=WCR2014 />。以全球而言，乳癌是女性癌症中最常見的，佔了25%，在2012年，有168萬的乳癌個案，及52萬人因乳癌死亡<ref name=WCR2014Epi>{{cite book|title=World Cancer Report 2014|date=2014|publisher=World Health Organization|isbn=9283204298|chapter=Chapter 1.1}}</ref>。乳癌在已開發國家較常見，且女性患乳癌的機率是男性的100倍<ref name=WCR2008 /><ref>{{Cite web | title = Male Breast Cancer Treatment | publisher = National Cancer Institute | year = 2014 | url = http://www.cancer.gov/cancertopics/pdq/treatment/malebreast/HealthProfessional | accessdate = 2014-06-29 | archive-date = 2014-07-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140704182515/http://www.cancer.gov/cancertopics/pdq/treatment/malebreast/HealthProfessional | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 症狀 ==

